{{version021}}
{{Flavour|Breathes a blast of fire at a targeted creature, leaving a cloud of flames at the endpoint.}}

'''Searing Breath''' is a monster-only ability that acts like [[Bolt of Fire]] or [[Fire Breath]], with the addition of placing a flame [[cloud]] at the end of the bolt. Having fire resistance helps mitigate the damage, as does not standing in the flames left behind.

